            { "id": "r12", "name": "replyText", "value": "🤖 *HRBot Commands*\n\n⏰ *checkin* — Mark arrival\n⏰ *checkout* — Mark departure\n📋 *my tasks* — View tasks\n📅 *apply leave* — Request leave\n📊 *leave balance* — Check days left\n❓ *help* — Show this menu\n\nPowered by Claude AI 🧠", "type": "string" }
